| `panel` | `#262A44` | Secondary surfaces (cards, forms) |
| `cyan` | `#00CFC8` | Accent & focus ring |
| `mag` | `#FF4DCC` | Accent 2 / gradient |
| `red` | `#E12121` | CTA heat / notification |
| `dusk` | `#47538F` | Primary dark-blue accent |
